and early work on North American species of 
<taxonomicName box="[511,585,1044,1069]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Geron" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[511,585,1044,1069]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">Geron</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
